---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
  <main>
    <div class="mx-auto md:max-w-3xl w-full px-10">
      <!-- Introduction Section -->
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Hello World! 👋</h1>
        <p>
          Welcome to my site !<br /> I'm Boris, a self-taught frontend and backend
          developer with a passion for crafting exceptional digital experiences and
          aan eating kibbles.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Passion for Purrfection -->
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">🌟 Passion for Purrfection</h2>
        <p>
          I take immense pride in my work, approaching each project with a
          relentless pursuit of purrfection. Whether it's crafting elegant code,
          designing intuitive user interfaces, or solving complex digital
          puzzles, I tackle it all with the grace and precision of a cat on the
          prowl.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 🚀 Boris: The Code Ninja -->
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">🚀 Boris: The Code Ninja</h2>
        <p>
          Picture this: a sleek cat with coding glasses perched on my whiskers,
          and a tail that wags with excitement for all things JavaScript. I'm
          not your average feline; I'm a code ninja, gracefully leaping from
          function to function in the digital dojo.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 🌐 Web Development, the Boris Way -->
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
          🌐 Web Development, the Boris Way
        </h2>
        <p>
          What sets us apart? Well, aside from my impeccable taste in tuna, it's
          our commitment to making web development as smooth as a cat's fur.
          Agile like a cheetah, responsive like a well-trained dog - we've got
          it all covered.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 🌌 Boris: The Byte Buccaneer -->
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">🌌 Boris: The Byte Buccaneer</h2>
        <p>
          Imagine a dashing feline pirate with a tricorn hat adorned with lines
          of code and a swashbuckling tail ready to conquer the high seas of web
          development. That's me, Boris, your trusty byte buccaneer, sailing
          through the binary waves.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  body {
    background-image: linear-gradient(#e0e0f4 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(to right, #e0e0f4 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 35px 35px;
    background-color: #fff;
  }

  .clip-path {
    clip-path: circle(50% at 50% 50%);
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }
</style>
